abstract: North Carolina, which returns all five starters from a team that reached the regional basketball finals last season, is the runaway No. 1 in the Associated Press men’s preseason top 25.
snippet: North Carolina, which returns all five starters from a team that reached the regional finals last season, is the runaway No. 1 in the Associated Press men’s preseason top 25, released Friday.
